      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This chassis has undergone proactive maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS unit overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to address common structural fatigue points. The suspension retains its original geometry for balanced turn-in response, while the braking system remains sharp with consistent pedal feel. Though the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals\u2014including rod bearing clearances\u2014are within spec, making this a mechanically sound platform for the purist.",
