      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power band peaking at an 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally sound, having received the essential rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term reliability. Power is routed through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a limited-slip differential. The suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the platform's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution and turn-in precision. While the finish shows minor cosmetic patina indicative of its age, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain geometry are dialed in for the serious driver.",
